title: DJ Walkman - Milk Und Herring MP3
description:
Mixed By: DJ Walkman
Title: Milk Und Herring 
Release date: 2008 05 22
Label: Sutemos.net
Catalogue #: Sutemosmix1

This release is protected with Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivs 2.5 License


The idea behind Milk Und Herring is really simple and well reflected in its title - to connect things that seem to be inconsistent from the first glance. And to do this as good as possible. because there is nothing worse than a monotonic mix that makes the listener die out of boredom. Enjoy!
